author: @jaypark9225
text:
4회까지 봤습니다. 평소 이런 드라마 안보는데 지나가다가 봤어요. 문제는 현타가 많이 오는 드라마라서 봅니다.
이태리 수입원단(생지) - 한국 가공 - 재수출  이딴거로 먹고 사는 인간으로 현타가 오고요, 원단 까대기 하는 인간으로 역시 현타가 옵니다.
수입, 수출, 컨테이너 부두, 창고, 수입반품 게다가 4화에 진선규 배우가 신발로 각종 테스트(못에 신발 내구력테스트 및 토치 방염 테스트) 하는데 또 역시 현타가 옵니다.
만화적 요소가 들어가 있지만 하이퍼 리얼리즘 이네요 누군가에겐.. ㅋㅋ
가장 큰 만화적 요인은, 이태리에 반품을 했는데 극에선 한 1~2주만에 배로 이태리 도착 - 절대 일어날 수 없는 일!! 그리고 컨테이너 부두에 가는 화물 주인들은 별로 없을듯요 ㅋ

author: @mini683
text:
I am a Malaysian, though Malaysia survived from 1997, but the economic recession hit everyone hard.

I was 26 years old in 1997, my father was not good at money control and I took over the car and house loan. 

The car loan interest was 12% for a loan period of 36 months from 1996 to 1998...

I can't remember how I survived with my family debts, but I did❤

Thanks to this drama, somehow it 's heal me❤

Love from Kuching, Malaysia.

author: @jeongahpark8902
text: 내가 IMF를 겪었던 나이가 딱 극속의 태풍이 나이였어요. 그 시절 고통스럽던 기억이 다시 떠오르기도 해서 드라마에 더 몰입해서 보게 됩니다. 그땐 출근하는 매일매일 물건 판 고객회사가 부도났다는 소식이 이어졌던 날들이었어요. 물건은 팔았는데 돈을 받을길이 없고, 그런 회사들은 하루하루 늘어만 가서 회사에서 밤새며 돈을 받아낼 수 있는 모든 방법들을 고민하고 대책을 마련하느라 집에도 못가고 아침이 오는게 두려운 날들이었지요. 또 다른 고객회사가 부도 났다는 소식을 접할게 뻔했으니까요. 고객사가 하나같이 이름있는 큰 회사들 이었답니다. 내가 좋아하는 준호가 주연인 것도 아름다운 준호의 목소리로 OST를 불러줘서 좋네요. 우리 젊은 청년들은 제발 IMF 같은건 안겪었으면 좋겠어요.

Did you see the rainbow?

Every time in the air at dawn
It feels like swimming with no end
In the story that makes no sense
Under the falling raindrops
I would fall into daydream

In the world of black and white
I want to fill this with colors once again
Did you see the rainbow?
At the other side of the purple,
The one I missed, are you there?
I just want the rainbow
Even if it takes a long way to go back

I believe in my shine every day☀️

If you know the whole translation of the song, please, share it❤
What a heartwarming song singing by our Sunshine Lee Junho ❤

author: @yaprakayse
text:
🌬️🎈 I can imagine: Sunset. The seashore. The wind blows gently. 

Seon: The wind always comes with you, Poong. When you find me, my hair gets messy but my heart finds order. 

Poong: Because there is a rope in your heart, Seon. No matter how much I drift, I always stay attached to that rope. 

Seon: Do you want to untie that rope? To fly… to be free? 

Poong: If I am going to fly without you, even the wind will scold me. 

A brief silence. A balloon floats on the horizon. The sun touches the water. 

Seon: Look, Poongseon… Our name floats in the sky. 

Poong: Yes. Together we are meaningful. On that thin line between the wind and the light. 

The balloon slowly drifts away. They watch it with their eyes. Seon reaches out her hand, Poong takes it. The wind caresses their hair. 

Seon: This is how we are, Poong. No matter how hard the wind blows, we are connected to each other with an invisible rope from our hearts. 

Poong: And thanks to that rope, the world becomes ours. 

The camera rises. On the horizon, the Poongseon balloon merges with the sky. The sky is still their color. 

The wind's name is Tae Poong, the light's name is Mi Seon. When mentioned together, the wind whispers a secret. #TyphoonFamily

author: @sunshit0125
text:
1화 엔딩은 임팩트가 어마어마 했다 태풍이의 허망 당혹 혼란 슬픔 여러감정이 뒤섞이다 무너져 내리는 엄마를보고 아버지가 가신걸 깨닫고 슬픔을 넘어서 텅빈 허망한 눈빛 그리고 그옆에 티비에선 imf가 흘러나오고 연기+연출+음악 다 갓벽했던 엔딩맛집 엔딩요정의 서막을 연 레전드 1화엔딩 이였다..이준호가 연기로 엔딩을 찢어👍👏

그러고 2화에서 또 레전드엔딩! 눈물의 벚꽃엔딩이 나왔지..😢🌸 철 없이 놀기 좋아했던 그치만 국내 1호 장미 강장미를🌹탄생 시킬 정도로 자신의 꿈을 키워오던 26살 태풍이가 자신의 꿈을 잠시 접어두고 아버지의 소중한 회사를 살리고 지켜 내겠다는 목표 하나만으로 사회로 뛰어들어 위기를 맞았을때 아버지와의 추억을 회상하며 꽃이 지는건 이기는거라던 아버지의 잘해낼거라는 이길수있다는 응원 처럼 눈발이 꽃잎이 휘날리는것처럼 보여지며 '이쁘다 아빠' 라며 아이처럼 울면서 웃는 태풍이 보며 또 오열😭 이준호 연기 넘 살발하게 잘해서 태풍이 개큰응원 하게돼😢 대성공해서 대박길 꽃길만걷자🌼🌸🌹

author: @미래김-z3p
text:
입봉작이라는데 작가 내공이 제법이네 티벤 올해 주말드 1회중 제일 잘 나왔다더니 간만에 따듯한 꿀잼 드라마라 이 작품 꽤 청률 잘 나오겠더라 16회 호흡이면 다음주 일요일이나 다담주부터 더 확 뛸듯..
감정선 필치도 섬세하고 떡밥회수도 잘되고...작가가 수상경력 있는 분이라더니 필력이 탄탄함
연출이야 뭐 워낙 유명한 쌈마 감독이라 연출 역량도 받쳐주는데다 감정선 몰입 제대로 돕는 오스트가 또 장난 아님ㅋㅋ달파란 맞는건가 느낌상 달파란 맞을거같은데 하나같이 다 적절한 타이밍에 감정선에 맞는 오스트를 제대로 까는 센스가ㅋㅋ음악들이 또 하나같이 좋다는게 함정임ㅋㅋ

text:
Felicitaciones por tu nueva serie.
Desde que escuché el tema en la serie "Did you see the rainbow", sabía que eras tú.
Tienes la virtud de que cuando lo escucho, me siento transportada a un lugar íntimo y acogedor y que esa voz, es de un xingu (amigo) o amor y que la comparte conmigo con toda sencillez y cariño.
Es un momento muy cálido y mi corazón agradece al escucharlo.
Gracias por regalarnos tu voz, tus dotes de bailarín y tu excelente performance en
#FamilyTypoon

Did you see the rainbow?

Every time in the air at dawn
It feels like swimming with no end
In the story that makes no sense
Under the falling raindrops
I would fall into daydream

In the world of black and white
I want to fill this with colors once again
Did you see the rainbow?
At the other side of the purple,
The one I missed, are you there?
I just want the rainbow
Even if it takes a long way to go back

I believe in my shine every day☀️


Our Sunshine Lee Junho's voice is heartwarming. ❤

text:
Mi-seon is the only one who has remained loyal to the company, but above all, she has trusted Tae-poong enough to trust him without any guarantees whatsoever. Their closeness came about naturally, due for both to their relationship with Kang Jin-young, her employer and his father, respectively. Together, they are working hard to resurface.

Anyway, Lee Joon-ho has such a bright smile that it's infectious, it makes you feel good right away. Kim Min-ha is always excellent, and she also infects you with her gorgeous smile and sweet face. They're very cute together; they make a great team.

author: @alexdequzman3990
text:
THIS VIDEO IS AWESOME! Thank you so much Junho, for letting us see the behind the scenes of the poster shoots for Typhoon Family! Also, for letting us inside the company office just to see you so happy with the rest of the employees! I had so much fun during this video. You look so handsome in suits that I can't help but smile everytime during the Content Shoot Day and during the premiere. Happy to see you working so hard but I wish that you still have enough time to rest.

Also I just finished watching Episode 1 and 2 of Typhoon Family. You did great as always! 👏👏👏🎉🎉🎉 I can't help but cry when Tae Pung's dad died and while he was reading the bankbook his father hid in his 'office safe' my tears just won't stop falling. 😭💔🤧 All the cast did amazing jobs portraying their character and my! I totally love the 90s fashion style of Tae Pung! 😍💖😎 That was so 🔥🔥🔥! His dancing and singing makes my heart dance! 💓💓💓💃💃💃 I love it so much! video_title: [태풍 홈비디오 #1] 나야 강태풍
author: @yaprakayse
text: At the beginning of the first episode, a smile first appears on your face… Then, little by little, you start to get to know Kang Tae Poong’s heart. You touch the values in his inner world, you build a closeness. True human purity is so rare, so precious. By the end of the episode, sadness fills you, but at the same time, there is a sense of completion… If there is love, if it’s felt, then nothing is truly left unfinished. Every incomplete relationship, every silent feeling, reaches wholeness with the right touch and at the end of this episode, Kang Tae Poong made me feel that. The moments when the boundary between the viewer and the character disappeared were magnificent. It wasn’t Lee Junho there it was Kang Tae Poong. In Typhoon Family, I found both the performances and the atmosphere of the era very successful. The whole cast performed wonderfully. And Lee Junho… his performance is so powerful that you want to lay all the flowers in the world along his path and thank him for his existence. Nice to meet you, Kang Tae Poong and #TyphoonFamily.
